    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intro</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After crash-landing on a newly discovered planet due to an electric shock, help Astri retrieve his data cards and complete the levels to reach his ship, in this “Die &amp; Retry” platformer from the Stellar Vault studio. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hard-to-complete single-player adventure awaits! With a variety of colorful skins and all the joy of level completion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258800/extras/3c782f7b0c358a32a8fc93cc7c876358.poster.avif?t=1748129484\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258800/extras/3c782f7b0c358a32a8fc93cc7c876358.webm?t=1748129484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 50 levels!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many levels in different ultra-challenging biomes, with achievements to complete. Retrieving all the data cards and finishing the game at 100% can only be done the bravest, most determined and most powerful people on earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dangers roam the planet</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware! You'll find robots that want to neutralize all unknown visitors (including you). Destroy them or use them as tools to complete the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258800/extras/5049fd5906c18eb8e153a2c186998988.poster.avif?t=1748129484\" width=590 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258800/extras/5049fd5906c18eb8e153a2c186998988.webm?t=1748129484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258800/extras/5049fd5906c18eb8e153a2c186998988.mp4?t=1748129484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple, accessible controls</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Just jump, run and dash - every key needs to be mastered which makes every fatal fall a lesson. Quick respawns encourage you to move on to discover the next levels and brave all their dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Student Project</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turned in as a student project for a video game development school in its first year, winning the jury's congratulations for its enormous content and “magnificent” animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Reimbursement for broken equipment due to excessive rage not taken into account :) ) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BYIYM</p>",
